trans-unit.source: Provides an extension point that can access member characteristics of a XAML member through techniques other than reflection.
trans-unit.target: Gir et utvidelsespunkt som har tilgang til medlemmet egenskaper for et medlem som XAML via teknikker enn gjenspeiling.

trans-unit.source: The purpose of XamlMemberInvoker is to enable an extensible XAML type system, schema, and a working run time that does not rely as fully on CLR features such as CLR attributes, reflection information through <xref:System.Type> and <xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo>, and so on.
trans-unit.target: Formålet med XamlMemberInvoker er å gi et omfattende XAML typen system, skjema og en fungerende kjøretid som ikke er avhengig som fullstendig CLR-funksjoner for eksempel CLR-attributter, gjenspeiling informasjon gjennom <xref:System.Type>og <xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo>og så videre.</xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo> </xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Subclasses of XamlMemberInvoker are used as input parameters for the alternate constructors of XAML schema classes such as <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>.
trans-unit.target: Underklasser av XamlMemberInvoker brukes som inndataparametere for alternativ konstruktører XAML skjemaet klasser som <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>

trans-unit.source: You subclass <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember> and pass the XamlMemberInvoker through to the base constructor.
trans-unit.target: Du deaktiverer <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>og sende XamlMemberInvoker via base-konstruktøren.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>

trans-unit.source: Along with defining a XamlMemberInvoker for the constructor, you must also provide overrides for at least some of the `Lookup` methods of <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>.
trans-unit.target: Tillegg definere en XamlMemberInvoker for konstruktøren, må du også angi overstyringer for til minst noen av de `Lookup` metoder for <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>

trans-unit.source: XamlMemberInvoker has a default implementation.
trans-unit.target: XamlMemberInvoker har en standard implementering.

trans-unit.source: The default implementation follows a similar model to the default implementation of XAML schema types <xref:System.Xaml.XamlType> and <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>: the CLR type system is used for instantiation, values and lookups, including using CLR attributes, <xref:System.Type> and <xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo>, and so on.
trans-unit.target: Standard implementering etter en lignende modell til standard implementering av XAML skjematypene <xref:System.Xaml.XamlType>og <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>: CLR-typen systemet brukes for instantiering, verdiene og oppslag, inkludert ved hjelp av CLR-attributter <xref:System.Type>og <xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo>og så videre.</xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo> </xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember> </xref:System.Xaml.XamlType>

trans-unit.source: XamlMemberInvoker provides methods for basic get and set operations (<xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.GetValue%2A>; <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.SetValue%2A>).
trans-unit.target: XamlMemberInvoker inneholder metoder for grunnleggende get og Sett inn (<xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.GetValue%2A>; <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.SetValue%2A>).</xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.SetValue%2A></xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.GetValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: It also provides the properties <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.UnderlyingGetter%2A> and <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.UnderlyingSetter%2A>, but these are not virtual.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg inneholder egenskapene <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.UnderlyingGetter%2A>og <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.UnderlyingSetter%2A>, men dette er ikke virtuelle.</xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.UnderlyingSetter%2A> </xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.UnderlyingGetter%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > It may be possible to obtain a XamlMemberInvoker value that represents a XAML directive, which is implemented as a private class in the System.Xaml implementation.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Det kan være mulig å hente en XamlMemberInvoker-verdi som representerer en XAML-direktivet som implementeres som en privat klasse i System.Xaml implementeringen.

trans-unit.source: If you attempt to call <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.GetValue%2A> or <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.SetValue%2A> on this invoker, an exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du prøver å kalle <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.GetValue%2A>eller <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.SetValue%2A>på denne anroperen et unntak.</xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.SetValue%2A> </xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.GetValue%2A>
